# Refinement: Real-time Sync, Order Preview & Quantity Control

Finalizing the hyperlocal delivery experience by adding missing UX elements, improving real-time reliability, and giving customers more control over their orders.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Order Acceptance**: Riders will now see an "Order Preview" screen before accepting. Direct "Accept" from the dashboard will be replaced with "View Details".
> - **Quantity Adjustment**: Customers can now decrease product quantity (e.g., from 5x to 3x) instead of just removing the entire item.

